# GitHub Actions workflows — the GitHub App token used by Claude Code lacks the
# `workflows` permission scope required to push these files. They live on disk
# at .github/workflows/ and must be pushed manually using a personal access token
# with the `workflow` scope:
#   git add .github/workflows/ && git push
.github/
